==English==
===Etymology===
Coined in [[w:1867|1867]]. Compound of ''[[blood]]'' and ''[[bath]],'' the latter used to refer in the metaphorical sense to a [[deluge]] of a thing.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# [[indiscriminate|Indiscriminate]] [[killing]] or [[slaughter]].

